    <about locale="en_US">
<![CDATA[
<p><b>ComfortBuy</b> is a universal design theme family for all basic Webasyst apps: Site, Blog, Photos, Shop-Script, and others. The parent (main) theme of the family, which includes the basic set of CSS rules and the common layout template index.html, is the ComfortBuy theme for the Site application. All ComfortBuy design themes used in other applications (e.g., Blog or Photos) utilize common CSS rules and file index.html of the parent (main) theme.</p>
<p>ComfortBuy design themes are optimized for all modern web browsers, including iOS and Android based mobile devices.</p>

